&lt;p>It funds world class scientific research on issues relating to economic development and quality of life in less developed countries with the potential for impact on policy and practice for poverty reduction.&lt;br />&amp;nbsp;&lt;br />The Strategic Advisory Team to the scheme will contribute to enhancing the impact of this successful and globally-respected research programme.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>

&lt;p>The team will build capacity to deliver impact for the scheme using three interlinked approaches; turning research into results, evaluation, and influencing and scaling up through communication.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p>

